    "body": "In your example, you have actually no sort so yes it's expected that the original order order is preserved.\r\n\r\nYou should consider here that the API does not provide any information or guarantees in this case. If it appears to sorted by refined first it is just a side effect of the implementation, not something done on purpose.\r\n\r\nI might have missed something but here that's not a bug to me. ",
